last_episode_to_air.name: Old Friends, New Frontiers
last_episode_to_air.overview: A risky operation is humanity’s best and last hope.

name: Invasion
overview: Earth is visited by an alien species that threatens humanity's existence. Events unfold in real time through the eyes of five ordinary people across the globe as they struggle to make sense of the chaos unraveling around them.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: The second season picks up just months later with the aliens escalating their attacks in an all-out war against the humans.

episodes.name: Last Day
episodes.overview: Across the globe, strange and unexplainable events begin to unfold. A small-town sheriff senses something bigger is at play.

episodes.name: Crash
episodes.overview: Amid chaos, Aneesha makes a difficult decision for the sake of her family. Trevante, a Navy SEAL, investigates a distress call with his team.

episodes.name: Orion
episodes.overview: Mitsuki takes desperate measures, determined to uncover the truth. Casper and Jamila discover just how dire their situation is.

episodes.name: The King Is Dead
episodes.overview: Trevante fears the worst until a locator beacon gives him hope. Mitsuki finds an ally in the most unexpected place.

episodes.name: Going Home
episodes.overview: The president of the United States gives an urgent global address in an attempt to prepare the world for what lies ahead.

episodes.name: Home Invasion
episodes.overview: In shock from the president’s speech, Aneesha rushes back to her family only to find their safe haven—and their lives—threatened.

episodes.name: Hope
episodes.overview: Mitsuki commandeers a satellite station, hoping to make contact with outer space. Caspar reveals a strange secret he thinks is related to the invasion.

episodes.name: Contact
episodes.overview: Trevante’s plane lands, but his journey home is just beginning. Caspar and Jamila brave London’s streets, trying to make sense of his secret.

episodes.name: Full of Stars
episodes.overview: Mitsuki is determined to contact the Hoshi 12 before it’s too late, as the military detains the Maliks and Caspar takes a risk that may kill him.

episodes.name: First Day
episodes.overview: The world, still reeling from global destruction, faces a new and unforeseen dawn.

episodes.name: Something's Changed
episodes.overview: Mitsuki is taken to an alien ship in the Amazon jungle. Aneesha and her children take refuge with a group called the Movement.

episodes.name: Chasing Ghosts
episodes.overview: At home in Miami, Trevante struggles with returning to day-to-day life. Similarly, Jamila feels an unceasing pull to search for Caspar.

episodes.name: Fireworks
episodes.overview: A game-changing discovery could finally give Earth an advantage. Aneesha finds it difficult to trust the Movement, despite needing their help.

episodes.name: The Tunnel
episodes.overview: Jamila's decision to trek the Channel Tunnel puts the group face-to-face with an even deadlier enemy.

episodes.name: A Voice from the Other Side
episodes.overview: Aneesha, Luke, and the Movement make a plan to locate Sarah. Mitsuki has a devastating encounter with the alien entity.

episodes.name: Pressure Points
episodes.overview: Jamila and the gang reach the hospital and find a surprise. En route to Camp Pierce, the Movement get caught in a savage attack.

episodes.name: Down the Rabbit Hole
episodes.overview: Trevante and Rose investigate a clue that leads them to Ben Shelton’s farm. Monty has suspicions about the mission and confides in Jamila.

episodes.name: Cosmic Ocean
episodes.overview: Mitsuki begins experiencing symptoms from her time with the alien entity. Nikhil breaks into the enclosure, setting off global seismic events.

episodes.name: Breakthrough
episodes.overview: A dangerous trip to the alien mothership results in a connection across dimensions.

episodes.name: Old Friends, New Frontiers
episodes.overview: A risky operation is humanity’s best and last hope.

2.overview: The second season picks up just months later with the aliens escalating their attacks in an all-out war against the humans.
